description.narrative: This activity (Procurement of Services-Civil Service Reform) is a component of Civil Service Reform Programme reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £3,166,700. This component benefits Ethiopia, and works in the following sector(s): Public sector policy and administrative management. , with the following implementing partners: Coffey International Development. The start date is 02-12-2006 and the end date is 30-03-2013.
